name: CYBERcube (itch) (ilya096, Foxeleos, x1xJoker)
description:
You are too weak to pass this, the Great Cube will only let the worthy one through!

The project is based on the Unreal Engine game Engine version 4.23.1. 3d models are created in the Blender 3d editor. During the development of the project, 5 cups of coffee, 6 cups of tea were drunk and 4 kilograms of pizza were eaten. 

We will continue development after voting period and will finish all feautures we did not complete in time!
